      "comment_id": 14116,
      "date": "2024-01-08T15:20:43",
      "author_name": "Jack'n'Jean",
      "content": "<p>Ich weiß nicht, ob es noch gesagt wurde: Das mit den Ausrufezeichen war ein Terry Pratchett-Zitat. Imho gehört es in eine Reihe mit weiteren großartigen Zitaten von ihm, wie: “There’s a certain type of manager who is known by his call of ‘My door is always open’ and it is probably a good idea to beat yourself to death with your own CV rather than work for him.”  oder &#8222;Even so, there is no excuse for putting pineapple on pizza.&#8220;</p>\n<div class=\"cld-like-dislike-wrap cld-template-2\">\n    <div class=\"cld-like-wrap  cld-common-wrap\">\n    <a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" class=\"cld-like-trigger cld-like-dislike-trigger  \" title=\"Mag ich!\" data-comment-id=\"14116\" data-trigger-type=\"like\" data-restriction=\"cookie\" data-already-liked=\"0\">\n                        <i class=\"fas fa-heart\"></i>\n                </a>\n    <span class=\"cld-like-count-wrap cld-count-wrap\">    </span>\n</div></div>",
